pic-ai/sdk`; user asks to use the Claude API, Anthropic SDKs, or Managed Agents (`/v1/agents`, `/v1/sessions`); user asks to add, modify, debug, optimize, or improve a Claude feature (prompt caching, cache hit rate, adaptive thinking, compaction, code_execution, batch, files API, citations, memory tool) or a Claude model (Opus/Sonnet/Haiku) in a file; or user asks about prompt caching / cache hit rate / cache reads / cache creation in any project that uses the Anthropic SDK (even without mentioning Claude by name).\nDO NOT TRIGGER when: file imports `openai`/non-Anthropic SDK, filename signals another provider (`agent-openai.py`, `*-generic.py`), code is provider-neutral, or task is general programming/ML.\n- metaswarm-setup: Metaswarm Guided Setup\n- metaswarm-update-version: Update Metaswarm","skillCount":8,"isInitial":true},"type":"attachment","uuid":"9bd85f6c-7461-4969-bf19-bf5137d03851","timestamp":"2026-04-14T00:36:22.051Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-cli","cwd":"/Users/ryota","sessionId":"ed13aca3-33f5-42cd-81a4-7500e1ed118d","version":"2.1.105","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
